xml: (info;sp)++separator, newline, soundMark*.

info: "("?, ~["()";#d;#a;'"']+, ")"?.
sp: (info, #9)?, speaker?, speech, "/", speech, tab?, controlChar*.
speaker: ["A"-"Z"], ~[#d;#a]+, -": ".
speech: q, ~[#d;#a]+, q.

-separator: newline+, (soundMark, newline)*.

-q: -'"'.
-soundMark: -" ()".
-newline: #d?, #a.
-tab: -#9.
-controlChar: -Cc.
{We're running into a problem with control characters.}